    "While we believe this analysis will provide valuable insights, to the best of our knowledge, no benchmarks currently exist for evaluating token-level rewards.",
    "Future work should focus on constructing dedicated evaluation datasets to facilitate quantitative assessment of token-level reward accuracy.",
    "Rewards in other levels.",
    "Our approach focuses on utilizing rewards at the token and sequence levels.",
    "However, intermediate levels, such as step-level and span-level rewards, also provide useful information for alignment tasks and have been widely applied, especially in math and coding problems."
